episodes.title: The Most DISTURBING Cults In History - Colonia Dignidad -Emma Watson
episodes.description: Join us in our new series as we explore the most terrifying cults in history. Uncover the shocking tale of Paul Schaefer, a man who evaded capture for eight years. His arrest revealed his involvement in the Pinochet regime's darkest deeds, from the disappearance of political prisoners to manufacturing weapons and more horrific acts. This story is one you can't miss. Watch now to learn the chilling truths, and don't forget to like, subscribe, and share your feelings about these sinister groups. We need your support to keep bringing these stories to light.
